            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-heading mb-4">
              2050 N 300 W<br />
              Hangar #122<br />
              Spanish Fork, UT 84660
            </p>
            <a 
              href="https://maps.google.com/?q=2050+N+300+W+Hangar+122+Spanish+Fork+UT+84660" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer" 
              class="inline-block text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-heading"
            >
              Get Directions ‚Üí
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 font-heading">
              Hours
            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-heading">
              Monday - Friday: 8am - 5pm<br />
              Saturday: 8am - 3pm<br />
